cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on automatic video caption generation, which involves natural language processing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper deals with video analysis and captioning, which involves visual recognition and understanding. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper evaluates two caption generation methods and discusses their performance. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper deals with automated caption generation. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video captioning, which is a multimedia task.
